  "title": "PA to MD - Full Secretarial Support / with Minutes Taking / Willing to Travel when Required - Alexandra Area",
  "description": "<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bilingual. Strong verbal and written communication skills, with proficiency in both languages</p></li><li><p>Ability to read and type in Traditional Chinese as required to communicate with China and Taiwan office</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel when required once in a while</p></li><li><p>High level of professionalism, discretion, and organisational skills.</p></li></ul><p><strong>JOB Duties & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide full-spectrum secretarial and administrative support to the Managing Director, including flight bookings, accommodation arrangements, transportation coordination, and schedule management.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and compile itineraries, reports, presentations, and business correspondence.</p></li><li><p>Organise and coordinate meetings, including preparing agendas, taking minutes, and following up on action items.</p></li><li><p>Liaise professionally with internal staff, external suppliers, and clients.</p></li><li><p>Provide personal assistance to top management when required, such as grocery purchases and coordination of household maintenance.</p></li><li><p>Perform any other ad-hoc tasks assigned by the Director.</p></li></ul><p><strong>JOB INFORMATION</strong></p><p><ul><li>Japanese MNC</li><li>Salary: S$4,000 – S$4,500</li><li>Annual Leave: 12 days</li><li>Working Hours: 9:00 am – 5:00 pm (Monday – Friday)</li><li>Bonus: Variable bonus based on performance (no AWS)</li><li>10 mins walk shelter all the way from Circle Line Labrador Park MRT Station</li></ul><p><br />Kindly send in your resume, we regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly.</p><p>EA License | 14C7092</p><p>EA Registration Number | R1110882 (Lee Ming Er)</p></p>",
